{"tid":125268,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「連兒子都不敢看我」　罕病男全身長滿瘤","createTime":"2017-02-18T10:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T21:09:30.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0521fc644517834f7b185ece26f213b4f1f4143","tid":125268,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:32:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i3/Dc7jp9.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi3%2FDc7jp9.png&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=d8c37d10\" target=\"_blank\">https://upload.cc/i3/Dc7jp9.png</a><br />\n<br />\n「連兒子都不敢看我」　罕病男全身長滿瘤<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170218/1058799/1/%E3%80%8C%E9%80%A3%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E6%95%A2%E7%9C%8B%E6%88%91%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E7%BD%95%E7%97%85%E7%94%B7%E5%85%A8%E8%BA%AB%E9%95%B7%E6%BB%BF%E7%98%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170218%2F1058799%2F1%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%2583%25BD%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2595%25A2%25E7%259C%258B%25E6%2588%2591%25E3%2580%258D%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%25BD%2595%25E7%2597%2585%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E7%2598%25A4&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=2651e2f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170218/1058799/1/%E3%80%8C%E9%80%A3%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E6%95%A2%E7%9C%8B%E6%88%91%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E7%BD%95%E7%97%85%E7%94%B7%E5%85%A8%E8%BA%AB%E9%95%B7%E6%BB%BF%E7%98%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i3/uDCmzr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi3%2FuDCmzr.png&h=2e2b52c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「連我12歲的大兒子，現在都不敢看我，也不願意和我說話」。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n孟加拉47歲男子侯賽因(Shadot Hossain)因為遺傳性疾病「神經纖維瘤症後群」(neurofibromatosis)，全身上下長滿了大大小小上千個腫瘤，由於無法抑制腫瘤到處增生，甚至長到眼睛，醫生警告他即將永久失明。<br />\n<br />\n侯賽因13歲時，在前額發現第一個腫瘤，當時並不以為意，早期也並未影響他的生活，直到最近5年，腫瘤大量瘋狂增生，現在他上半身完全無法穿衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，腫瘤遮住他的雙眼、嘴部，連進食都非常困難，他的妻子表示，侯賽因已經幾乎失去自理生活的能力，無法自己吃飯更衣，連上廁所都必須家人在旁幫忙。另外，因為他無法工作，完全沒有收入，都要靠妻子打零工貼補家用，更別說龐大的醫療費用。<br />\n<br />\n侯賽因難過地說：「我完全不能出門，因為附近的孩子看到我就被嚇哭，他們叫我『怪物』，我自己的3個孩子也怕我，不和我說話，這樣的痛苦是難以忍受的」。當地一名醫師知道他的狀況後，主動替他在網路上發起募款，陸續獲得善心人士資助，侯賽因準備前往達卡，接受一個醫療志工單位的贊助，進行全身檢查，希望能緩解他的痛苦。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"a405254c8f3ef2e69157f40ea08235161c233197","tid":125268,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"丁左<br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"35fe4003efc084dfa3ad5dcec62f8ed99f79830f","tid":125268,"uid":5292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:34:07.000Z","msg":"有老婆也是神蹟"},{"pid":"b06d921283f8401efcdf1ed446f9807aa2fa9b9e","tid":125268,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:35:30.000Z","msg":"clicker<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c7a12c943562b2427da75e29ff46158fcee981","tid":125268,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:36:11.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母"},{"pid":"ca5093bb7f66a8189f5b972f3d7d9ddfc5d5bf9a","tid":125268,"uid":28966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:36:54.000Z","msg":"大個d好似春袋"},{"pid":"73a8feb767d23a7e8733b59590a84faf569d77e6","tid":125268,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">慎入</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170218/420_832bdcc6d7a3eb251e21e039b46b498c.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170218%2F420_832bdcc6d7a3eb251e21e039b46b498c.j